---
// Giscus comments — each page maps to a GitHub Discussion (by pathname) in the
// "Announcements" category, which visitors can't post to directly, so threads
// can only be created by the giscus app. Requires the giscus GitHub App
// (https://github.com/apps/giscus) to be installed on ehabterra/go-reference.
// Reactions are off here — the page already has its own like button.
---
<section class="dp-comments">
  <h2 class="dp-comments__title">Comments</h2>
  <p class="dp-comments__hint">Sign in with GitHub to join the discussion.</p>
  <script
    is:inline
    src="https://giscus.app/client.js"
    data-repo="ehabterra/go-reference"
    data-repo-id="R_kgDOSyOa0g"
    data-category="Announcements"
    data-category-id="DIC_kwDOSyOa0s4C_BbT"
    data-mapping="pathname"
    data-strict="0"
    data-reactions-enabled="0"
    data-emit-metadata="0"
    data-input-position="top"
    data-theme="transparent_dark"
    data-lang="en"
    data-loading="lazy"
    crossorigin="anonymous"
    async></script>
</section>
